{"tid":1379234,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[宣傳]滑板有三好,我真希望街上可以多一D","createTime":"2019-07-28T18:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:30:19.000Z","uid":264797,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"640f51bb6d28c28c8e521c87b6120db01b3a3ebd","tid":1379234,"uid":264797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:12:31.000Z","msg":"吹水台太易沉,所以另開<br />\n帶出街方便,一手拿起<br />\n代步,廣告牌,運輸 都得<br />\n玩花式,代步亦得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBBicij.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBBicij.jpg&h=ca326193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AYkqDj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0AYkqDj.jpg&h=978ac97d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSnUu4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSnUu4Z.jpg&h=f94f4328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tO18LxucLt0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtO18LxucLt0&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=0414e18f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tO18LxucLt0</a><br />\n運輸效果係冇板車,手推車,積車咁架拉但勝在方便<br />\n一架可以負重90KG以內,搬野得<br />\n<br />\n但玩滑板時,記得帶頭盔同護膝,唔係會受傷<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GcLFpzicks4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGcLFpzicks4&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=bedf3c73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GcLFpzicks4</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人咁有創意,買淨色或者係純木既滑板板面就FIT哂<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aurzzaIHu2Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaurzzaIHu2Y&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=6f3f10be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aurzzaIHu2Y</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知點玩,唔怕,YOUTUBE 有教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p3NXd3DhH08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp3NXd3DhH08&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=69c3ae2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p3NXd3DhH08</a><br />\n學埋豚跳,跳過路面隙縫無難度<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dVRY6jXoPGE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdVRY6jXoPGE&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=20517d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dVRY6jXoPGE</a><br />\n<br />\n唔建議新手玩魚仔板,又細又難平衡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1uvNRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1uvNRE.jpg&h=38524f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔建議電子板,一來貴,二來重,三來犯法,<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7vVYYj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7vVYYj.jpg&h=e95550a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔見心痛,新手難控制,而且始終係用電,冇電就廢左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZihQNRE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZihQNRE.png&h=7ebdf70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n硬摝通常係花式比較好用,軟轆比較岩踩街,轆既大小都會影響表現架<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C-A8FBKNPdY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC-A8FBKNPdY&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=ed15c552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C-A8FBKNPdY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOqyLEy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOqyLEy.jpg&h=a01cfddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/search?Ntt=skateboard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.decathlon.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fsearch%3FNtt%3Dskateboard&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=23e96d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/search?Ntt=skateboard</a><br />\n係DECATHLON買,六百蚊有找,雖然冇淨色板(小聲:噴下咪黑色LO<br />\n純木既要有8five2shop,hkit,skatecity 呢D滑板店,或者淘寶(個人會推薦SKATECITY,質素比前面差少少,但勝在價錢比較便<br />\n有興趣既可以GOOGLE下架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係咩?<br />\n香港係未有明確法例唔比滑板係路上出現(除非炒板傷到人<br />\n<br />\n見到街上咁多人跑到身水身汗,而你都淨係塊板上面,慳幾多力,速度又快D<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">極度反對係市區玩,車多人多狗又多,傷到人就唔好拉!!!</span></span><br />\n但真係好想睇到<span style=\"color: red;\">百人滑板團</span><br />\n岩岩學踩板,有小小心得純分享,希望各位支持和補充"},{"pid":"8d1fbae46875fdd8f55af41dc98fb254ebac9b5d","tid":1379234,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:16:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f14a6169baa23805bf765359c2b20d81bcb2e73f","tid":1379234,"uid":239496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:19:29.000Z","msg":"貴唔貴"},{"pid":"fe9503341cb5ca003e8f64ee33eae1f8ed36c3a2","tid":1379234,"uid":264797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f14a6169baa23805bf765359c2b20d81bcb2e73f","tid":1379234,"uid":239496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:19:29.000Z","msg":"貴唔貴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:24:50.000Z","msg":"$1000-500以下都有<br />\n但用左一定有用"},{"pid":"a6bbc483a4ce44edc1f6dc5fc9c48bb7061659a4","tid":1379234,"uid":264797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afeb087157771988353a8fbea844c8f5b0bc5fa","tid":1379234,"uid":264797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"778832fca81c7818f40195d31b1fe2849080422c","tid":1379234,"uid":127244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"640f51bb6d28c28c8e521c87b6120db01b3a3ebd","tid":1379234,"uid":264797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:12:31.